By default, the image loads the `.htpasswd` file from the persistent data volume (i.e. from `/data/.htpasswd`). To change the location of this file, set the environment variable `PASSWORD_FILE` to the path of the `.htpasswd` file. Please note that this path must be accessible from inside the container and should be persisted. This is normally done by `nullfs(4)`-mounting a path into the container or with another appjail volume.
